Title: 一笑江湖 (DJ弹鼓版)
Artist: 闻人听書_
description: lyric with original chinese (simplified) transcription and pinyin transliteration, accompanying english translation


江湖一笑浪滔滔红尘尽忘了 俱往矣何足言道
jiānghú yīxiào làng tāotāo hóngchén jǐn wàngle jù wǎng yǐ hé zú yán dào
The world is filled with smiles and waves, and the world is forgotten. What is the point of saying that

苍天一笑笑不豪情却会了 对月饮一杯寂寥
cāngtiān yīxiào xiào bù háoqíng què huìle duì yuè yǐn yībēi jìliáo
The sky smiles but does not know how to be passionate. Drink a cup of lonely and lonely for the moon

剑起江湖恩怨拂袖罩明月 西风叶落花谢枕刀剑难眠
jiàn qǐ jiānghú ēnyuàn fúxiù zhào míngyuè xīfēng yè luòhuā xiè zhěn dāojiàn nán mián
The sword rises and the grudges of the rivers and lakes are blowing their sleeves to cover the bright moon, the west wind leaves fall and the flowers fade, the pillow is hard to sleep

汝为山河过客却总长叹伤离别 鬓如霜一杯浓烈
rǔ wèi shānhé guòkè què zǒng chángtàn shāng líbié bìn rú shuāng yībēi nóngliè
You are a passerby in the mountains and rivers, but you always sigh and part with you. Your temples are as thick as a cup of frost



只身走过多少的岁月看惯刀光照亮过黑夜
zhīshēn zǒuguò duōshǎo de suìyuè kàn guàn dāo guāng zhào liàngguò hēiyè
How many years have passed by alone? Watch the sword light illuminate the dark night

侠骨魔心如何来分辨弹指一梦不过一瞬间
xiágǔ mó xīn rúhé lái fēnbiàn tánzhǐ yī mèng bùguò yī shùnjiān
How to distinguish the magic heart of the chivalrous bones and demons in a flash of fingers and dreams in a flash

黄沙之中的残阳如血多少魂魄在此地寂灭
huáng shā zhī zhōng de cányáng rú xuè duōshǎo húnpò zài cǐdì jì miè
How many souls are silent here in the setting sun in the yellow sand

这成败有谁来了解
zhè chéngbài yǒu shéi lái liǎojiě
Who knows the success or failure of this

江湖一笑浪滔滔红尘尽忘了 俱往矣何足言道
jiānghú yīxiào làng tāotāo hóngchén jǐn wàngle jù wǎng yǐ hé zú yán dào
