也曾横刀向天笑数过路迢迢 数不完夕阳晚照
yě céng héng dāo xiàng tiān xiào shù guòlù tiáotiáo shǔ bù wán xīyáng wǎn zhào
I also laughed at the sky with my sword and counted the distances, and I could not count the sunset and night lights

苍天一笑乐逍遥江湖人自扰 留不住爱恨离潮
cāngtiān yīxiào lè xiāoyáo jiānghú rén zì rǎo liú bù zhù ài hèn lí cháo
The sky smiles happily and freely people in the world, and they can't keep love and hate and leave the tide
